{"tid":516644,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇腸胃科醫生介紹","createTime":"2018-01-01T15:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T06:44:47.000Z","uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fb6d24fe634fad4b23fdff9cdebcc620306e570a","tid":516644,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n成日個肚都好多氣<br />\n又冇胃口好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經睇過中醫同西醫"},{"pid":"c6c03ca8b9e6c53e9da55c5b523eaa7527411661","tid":516644,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"胃癌"},{"pid":"7c7546792c4cf37bf21401e1f3e2c0779d28c34a","tid":516644,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"316c381cfa1997dfaf842f8eb44ca1430a5e55cf","tid":516644,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"我以前都試過咁<br />\n到最後發現係胃氣多&amp;胃酸過多。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d21a5e34c3c34e169249298c946107f1e4dff9","tid":516644,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:26:30.000Z","msg":"試下食野慢d同食下乳酸菌幫助消化<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之前都係咁但食野慢d真係有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之前睇個家庭科醫生教我腸胃唔掂可以飲多d無糖熱檸水<br />\n食完飯飲一杯<br />\n之後用到無乜味就成片檸檬食左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乳酸菌就藥房買<br />\n真係好多氣好滯就食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132d7cf11ebe854ea732eb6dcee33acc55d3dc00","tid":516644,"uid":129925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"成日 肚柯之前 <br />\n但唔肚痛  <br />\n同好多爛屎  <br />\n有同路人嗎"},{"pid":"6c94ab62a111cb22053037be3294f9f99a3758ab","tid":516644,"uid":37380,"like":0,